{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00438/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00438"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:04:38"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman speaks to a man."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00438","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00438"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1/40b6166e-e32c-432e-ade9-0ebf6be14037","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:28:40.671Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>What is allowed at the breakfast table is largely determined by Reynolds’s mood and appetite. When depressed and overwrought from stress, he refuses these “stodgy things.” When hungry—sexually, creatively, literally—he devours them.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:873.2565789473686,756.5899122807019,503.5307017543861,293.1798245614034"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1/292a5f99-c6f4-4833-9a6c-0f577cfe4665","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:28:56.255Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Johanna's dress is an inversion of many of the dresses Alma wears throughout the film. The base color of her dress is red, like Alma's <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW18264239 BCX0\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01250.html\"><u>waitress outfit</u></a>, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW18264239 BCX0\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01735.html\"><u>first date dress</u></a>, and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW18264239 BCX0\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-04303.html\"><u>fashion show gown</u></a> (among others). However, Johanna's dress has black detailing while each of Alma's incorporates white. Alma brings a new lightness to Reynold's life while Johanna only bogs him down. Her collar is sharply downturned while Alma's either sweeps upward or covers her neck, a reflection of Johanna's sharp looks and \"confrontational\" questions against Alma's soft smiles and bashful gazes. The angular black lines covering Johanna's dress oppose the delicacy of the white lace on Alma's fashion show gown or the small ruffle on the collar of the first date dress. Alma's costumes combine simplicity with elegance, attractive traits to Reynolds, whereas the harsh patterns of Johanna's dress mirror her inability to blend into Reynolds' life.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:539.9671052631579,489.2872807017544,693.7828947368421,238.0372807017544"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1/d4d35f03-cbc6-460c-a99f-05de84dd9232","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:29:14.841Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Even in this shot, Johanna stands out against the delicate wallpaper of Reynolds' dining room. Meanwhile, at the scene of her introduction, Alma's waitress outfit <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW154112558 BCX0\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01326.html\"><u>balances the competing interior design features</u></a> of the restaurant.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00438/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:226.3048245614035,74.62719298245614,371.2171052631579,357.70833333333337"}}}]}]}]}